Steps.Message: Update at 08:09 - We're really sorry we're still not able to provide a timescale. As work progresses on site, our engineers will do the best they can to provide a revised estimated time for your power to be back on. With the cold weather, we understand that it can be very concerning to have a power cut as this may have affected your heating. If you have someone in the property who may be more vulnerable to the cold please do not hesitate to call us free on 105. We will do our best to provide additional care and support whilst work continues to get your power back on asap.
